name: Mysterious pumpkins
description:
Animation with all the pumpkins from the Halloween collection "Mysterious pumpkins" 2021.

This is my first collection that I created. It is timed to celebrate Halloween 2021. Each pumpkin has its own distinctive feature. There are eight in total + one animated one. Use them for Twitter avatars.

This item will be sent as a gift to those people who have helped me on my NFT journey.
